  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>YOU ARE ABOUT TO SEE A SCARY WORLD.</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3416560/extras/b7352161b7f932b068339d7b3bf214c0.poster.avif?t=1737557635\" width=738 height=502 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3416560/extras/b7352161b7f932b068339d7b3bf214c0.webm?t=1737557635\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3416560/extras/b7352161b7f932b068339d7b3bf214c0.mp4?t=1737557635\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i><strong>CAN YOU DISCOVER ITS SECRET?</strong></i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Scary World</i> is a single player bullet heaven roguelike. It's sort of like <i>Vampire Survivors</i> but with lots of physics, and surprises! Also, matches are shorter - you win if you can survive for 10 minutes. <strong><i>Give it a try, maybe you'll like it!</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3416560/extras/beaad24fd7f3865f8bcb2e6c66c935e6.poster.avif?t=1737557635\" width=800 height=568 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3416560/extras/beaad24fd7f3865f8bcb2e6c66c935e6.webm?t=1737557635\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3416560/extras/beaad24fd7f3865f8bcb2e6c66c935e6.mp4?t=1737557635\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Seven unlockable characters each with their own unique special powers</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over a dozen unique monsters that provide a different kind of challenge</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over a dozen learnable powers that work totally different from each other:</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >+ A lance that deals more damage the faster you're going</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >+ A stake that shoots downward below you, dealing critical damage that bypasses shields</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >+ A green shell that bounces around (watch out!)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >+ \"Laser Champ\", a floating laser eyeball who flies around helpin' you shoot these scary skeletons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >+ A shotgun!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >+ and many more!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SECRETS! The level of Scary World has many different kinds of secrets to uncover! Can you find them?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cheat codes!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Achievements!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Endless challenge, with 10 difficulty modes</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3416560/extras/01e32c4b9b0f60d11ddf460b58da4cea.avif?t=1737557635\" width=296 height=292 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The above image depicts the <strong>M424 Laser Champ</strong>, the friendly robot eyeball who has AI controlled Positronic Brain that shoots lasers at anything scary that he might see.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"It might not seem that scary to you, but if you were actually there it would be very scary I think\"</i> - quote from the developer</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3416560/extras/c2352c98e7ffad9dbf931b18e29f40b2.poster.avif?t=1737557635\" width=640 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3416560/extras/c2352c98e7ffad9dbf931b18e29f40b2.webm?t=1737557635\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3416560/extras/c2352c98e7ffad9dbf931b18e29f40b2.mp4?t=1737557635\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Come by the kbgames discord and share your thoughts and questions!</p>",
